---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="First Light Festival | Case Study | Adam Barnes"
  description="Case study: festival and event photography for First Light Festival since 2019, beach, stage, backstage, portraits and press calls on the Suffolk coast."
  canonical="https://www.adambarnes.biz/case-study-firstlight-festival.html"
  ogDescription="Festival and event photography for First Light Festival since 2019, beach, stage, backstage, portraits and press calls on the Suffolk coast."
  ogImage="https://www.adambarnes.biz/assets/og-image.jpg"
  ogType="article"
  bodyClass="page-photography"
  active="clients"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "CreativeWork",
    "name": "First Light Festival Photography",
    "creator": {
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "Adam Barnes",
      "url": "https://www.adambarnes.biz"
    },
    "description": "Annual festival and event photography for First Light Festival since 2019, covering the beach, stages, backstage, portraits, press calls and wider programme events across Suffolk.",
    "keywords": ["Festival Photography", "Event Photography", "First Light Festival", "Suffolk", "Lowestoft", "Portrait Photography"]
  }
  </script>
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.adambarnes.biz/"},
      {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Clients", "item": "https://www.adambarnes.biz/clients.html"},
      {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "First Light Festival", "item": "https://www.adambarnes.biz/case-study-firstlight-festival.html"}
    ]
  }
  </script>
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "First Light Festival — Photography Case Study",
    "description": "Case study: festival and event photography for First Light Festival since 2019 — beach, stage, backstage, portraits and press calls on the Suffolk coast.",
    "about": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "First Light Festival"
    },
    "url": "https://www.adambarnes.biz/case-study-firstlight-festival.html",
    "author": {
        "@type": "Person",
        "name": "Adam Barnes",
        "url": "https://www.adambarnes.biz"
    },
    "publisher": {
        "@type": "Person",
        "name": "Adam Barnes",
        "url": "https://www.adambarnes.biz"
    },
    "datePublished": "2026-04-01",
    "dateModified": "2026-04-23"
}
  </script>
  </Fragment>

<main>

    <!-- Page header -->
    <header class="section-header webdesign-header cs-header">
      <div class="cs-header-text">
        <h1 class="section-title">
          <span>First Light</span>
          <span class="accent">Festival</span>
          <span class="by-line">by Adam</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="section-intro">
          <span class="intro-lead">Every year since 2019, on the most easterly beach in the UK.</span>
          Six years of festival photography for First Light: from the beach at sunrise to the wings of the stage, backstage portraits, press calls, pavilion performances and events across the county.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-header-logo" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="assets/logos/first-light-festival-2026.svg" alt="" class="cs-header-logo-img">
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Case study body -->
    <section class="cs-body reveal" aria-label="Case study detail">
      <div class="cs-body-inner">

        <!-- Meta strip -->
        <div class="cs-meta">
          <div class="cs-meta-item">
            <span class="cs-meta-label">Client</span>
            <span class="cs-meta-value">First Light Festival</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-meta-item">
            <span class="cs-meta-label">Ongoing since</span>
            <span class="cs-meta-value">2019</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-meta-item">
            <span class="cs-meta-label">Services</span>
            <span class="cs-meta-value">Festival Photography · Event Photography · Portraits · Press Calls</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Narrative -->
        <div class="cs-copy">
          <div class="cs-copy-col">
            <h2 class="cs-copy-heading">The brief</h2>
            <p>First Light is one of those events where the setting does half the work and the photographer has to keep up with the other half. A free beach festival on the Suffolk coast, timed around the summer solstice, with music, arts and community at its core.</p>
            <p>The brief from the start was to document it properly. Not a highlights reel, but images that capture what the event actually feels like to be at. The same photographer covers the beach at dawn, the backstage corridors, the press calls and the pavilion programme, because consistency of eye across all of it is what makes the work useful across print, social and press.</p>
            <p>Since 2019 the commission has grown beyond the main festival to include other events across the county, giving First Light a body of photography that reflects the full breadth of what they do.</p>

            <h2 class="cs-copy-heading">The work</h2>
            <p><a href="photography.html#music-events">Festival photography</a> works when the photographer stops being a visitor with a camera. After six years, the rhythms of First Light are familiar: where the light falls on the beach at a particular hour, which moments are worth waiting for, which performances reward being close rather than back.</p>
            <p>Coverage across the years has included:</p>
            <ul class="cs-list">
              <li>The festival beach at sunrise</li>
              <li>Main stage and acoustic performances</li>
              <li>Backstage access and artist portraits</li>
              <li>Press calls and media events</li>
              <li>The pavilion programme</li>
              <li>Additional events across Suffolk</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-copy-col">
            <h2 class="cs-copy-heading">The outcome</h2>
            <p>The images are used across First Light's print materials, social channels and press output. When other organisations ask First Light for a photographer recommendation, they put Adam's name forward first.</p>
            <p>That is the kind of outcome you work six years to earn.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Gallery -->
        <div class="photo-grid cs-photo-grid">

          <div class="photo-item">
              <img src="assets/casestudies/firstlight/1Firstlight.webp" alt="First Light Festival" width="1200" height="573">
              <div class="photo-overlay"><span class="photo-caption">First Light Festival</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="photo-item">
              <img src="assets/casestudies/firstlight/2Firstlight.webp" alt="First Light Festival" width="1200" height="800">
              <div class="photo-overlay"><span class="photo-caption">First Light Festival</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="photo-item">
              <img src="assets/casestudies/firstlight/3Firstlight.webp" alt="First Light Festival" width="800" height="1200">
